Conviction locks do overlap and are not: Conviction locks do overlap and are not additive, meaning that funds locked during a previous vote can be locked again.
Endorsing a proposal that indicates your: Endorsing a proposal that indicates your backing for the proposal. Proposals with greater interest moves up the queue for potential next referendums.
If this proposal is passed, the changes: If this proposal is passed, the changes will be applied via dispatch and the deposit returned.
Select the committee account you wish to: Select the committee account you wish to make the proposal with.
Submit an Aye vote alongside the proposa: Submit an Aye vote alongside the proposal as part of a batch
The associated deposit for this proposal: The associated deposit for this proposal should be more then the minimum on-chain deposit required. It will be locked until the proposal passes.
The balance associated with the vote wil: The balance associated with the vote will be locked as per the conviction specified and will not be available for transfer during this period.
The calculated storage costs based on th: The calculated storage costs based on the size and the per-bytes fee.
The deposit will be locked for the lifet: The deposit will be locked for the lifetime of the proposal.
The external proposal to send to the tec: The external proposal to send to the technical committee
The hash of the preimage for the proposa: The hash of the preimage for the proposal as previously submitted or intended.
The image (proposal) will be stored on-c: The image (proposal) will be stored on-chain against the hash of the contents.
The proposal is in the queue for future: The proposal is in the queue for future referendums. One proposal from this list will move forward to voting.
The proposal will be registered from thi: The proposal will be registered from this account and the balance lock will be applied here.
The vote will be recorded for this accou: The vote will be recorded for this account. If another account delegated to this one, the delegated votes will also be counted.
The voting period and delay to apply to: The voting period and delay to apply to this proposal. The threshold is calculated from these values.
This account will pay the fees for the p: This account will pay the fees for the preimage, based on the size thereof.
When submitting a proposal the hash need: When submitting a proposal the hash needs to be known. Proposals can be submitted with hash-only, but upon dispatch the preimage needs to be available.
